{"tid":1988089,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無委任證自稱警員男子入賓館　偷住客數千元","createTime":"2020-04-25T03:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T03:35:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d664ee5b51deb8e9ae8c044ea72041331aa81c","tid":1988089,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T03:20:33.000Z","msg":"凌晨零時許，油麻地彌敦道328號15樓一間賓館，有一名中年漢向一名46歲韓姓女住客訛稱是警員，要求查看住客身分證，然後離去。住客其後發現約2500元現金不翼而飛，懷疑被人盜去，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查，案件列冒充警務人員及盜竊，交由油尖警區刑事調查隊第7隊跟進，暫未有人被捕，正追緝一名年約40至50歲、中等身材、蓄短黑髮男子，案發時他身穿黑色長袖上衣及黑色長褲、戴口罩，並攜有一個黑色斜揹袋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200425/s00001/d52e5838d01b15aeee2c1d12dd95a2db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200425%2Fs00001%2Fd52e5838d01b15aeee2c1d12dd95a2db.jpg&h=11306c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200425/s00001/1587777660685/%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E5%86%92%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%A5%E8%B3%93%E9%A4%A8-%E5%81%B7%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200425%2Fs00001%2F1587777660685%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%2586%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%25B3%2593%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E5%2581%25B7%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2585%2583&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKt9ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=68065168\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200425%2Fs00001%2F1587777660685%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%2586%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%25B3%2593%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E5%2581%25B7%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2585%2583&h=8837d898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81